Title: Clear search query also on-click
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1608034623
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

The last typed search query was already cleared if the results were selected with arrow keys and followed by enter or if directly pressed enter.
Now, they are also cleared when a result is selected by a mouse click.
